{"tid":622712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無安排傳媒隨團採訪","createTime":"2018-04-09T11:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T11:26:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"88460c00c92a528c7e0d99be04ca8592d7c91ddb","tid":622712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:06:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20355863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20355863&d=VPqP6xKM9lOwx49ngsWX2PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e2b1a8b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180409%2F20355863&h=0d0244d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180409/20355863</a><br />\n<br />\n無安排傳媒隨團採訪<br />\n<br />\n11.6K<br />\n要聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180409/large/09la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180409%2Flarge%2F09la2p2.jpg&h=ca6c84a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港珠澳大橋人工島被質疑防波堤崩塌。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】人工島疑似崩堤事件，引起香港社會對港珠澳大橋質量的疑慮，香港特區政府昨終派出路政署長鍾錦華到珠海了解事件。鍾昨晨先到港珠澳大橋管理局位於珠海香洲的辦事處，與管理局代表會面，隨後與大橋管理局人員到大橋東人工島視察，但香港和內地政府無就今次視察安排傳媒隨團採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n管理局人員首現身解畫<br />\n<br />\n路政署昨日傍晚亦就傳媒查詢發稿，但未有透露任何細節，僅稱署長鍾錦華昨在珠海與港珠澳大橋管理局會面，並指路政署整理資料後，將於今日會見傳媒。<br />\n<br />\n防波堤事件曝光後，傳媒除以電話聯絡大橋管理局職員，大橋管理局亦只在官方網站發稿回應。香港傳媒昨只能在大橋管理局辦事處門外等候，方有港珠澳大橋管理局副局長余烈現身回應事件，是事件發生後首次有管理局人員現身解畫。大橋管理局工程總監張勁文亦有接受傳媒訪問，認同外界對人工島防波堤的反應「誇張了」，認為從工程角度看，管理局日前發表的兩份文件已經解釋了外界疑慮。但他亦透露正準備書面材料，再向外解釋有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n登大橋人工島視察　路署今交代情況管理局：風浪細毋須整齊放弱波石<br />\n<br />\n要聞 10小時前"},{"pid":"de3bf7559f05180ec7da0118466b94d6810dbc0e","tid":622712,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b1abaa094e973ba12f2c4902e21c3165e292298","tid":622712,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大陸嗰邊會唔會死要臉, 堅持保持而家呢種排法呢?"},{"pid":"df81f1278c1025e91485449a021e53ec14d48e00","tid":622712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1abaa094e973ba12f2c4902e21c3165e292298","tid":622712,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大陸嗰邊會唔會死要臉, 堅持保持而家呢種排法呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺 D100 聽到有人打上去話唔係沖散,  係排齊之後專登拎開佢,  <br />\n<br />\n係話條隧道之前不停漏水."},{"pid":"6e2534951a5d288504f065d6647d6bebfbf486b4","tid":622712,"uid":20074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"沒事兒，沒事兒<br />\n死不了人<br />\n中國工程的質量是世界第一，咱們要對國家有信心"},{"pid":"fb0d5c6f7a67311924ad5ceae1cfe4b8872f62a2","tid":622712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df81f1278c1025e91485449a021e53ec14d48e00","tid":622712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b1abaa094e973ba12f2c4902e21c3165e292298","tid":622712,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔知大陸嗰邊會唔會死要臉, 堅持保持而家呢種排法呢?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱喺 D100 聽到有人打上去話唔係沖散,  係排齊之後專登拎開佢,  <br />\n<br />\n係話條隧道之前不停漏水."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"因為隧道下邊係淤泥"},{"pid":"0028fe0e10dc4001005062b0352d5c5509a48931","tid":622712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:26:43.000Z","msg":"玩完喇,  隧道無野壓住又會浮起斷裂<br />\n<br />\n壓佢又因為下邊有淤泥下沉."}]}